# Planning Mode Visual Map

This visual map outlines the systematic approach to planning features and changes in the AgenticFleet project.

## Planning Workflow Overview

<mermaid>
graph TD
    Start["🚀 START PLANNING MODE"] --> Assess["📊 Assess Task<br>Requirements"]
    Assess --> AnalyzeCode["👁️ Analyze Existing<br>Code"]
    
    AnalyzeCode --> DetermineScope["📏 Determine<br>Scope"]
    DetermineScope --> DetermineLevel{"🔍 Determine<br>Complexity Level"}
    
    %% Level 1 Planning
    DetermineLevel -->|"Level 1<br>Quick Fix"| L1["🔧 Level 1:<br>Simple Planning"]
    L1 --> L1Problem["🔍 Identify<br>Specific Issue"]
    L1Problem --> L1Solution["💡 Define<br>Simple Solution"]
    L1Solution --> L1Approach["📋 Create<br>Brief Plan"]
    
    %% Level 2 Planning
    DetermineLevel -->|"Level 2<br>Feature Enhancement"| L2["🛠️ Level 2:<br>Feature Planning"]
    L2 --> L2Reqs["📝 Document<br>Requirements"]
    L2Reqs --> L2Design["🎨 Create<br>Basic Design"]
    L2Design --> L2Tasks["📋 Define<br>Implementation Tasks"]
    L2Tasks --> L2Tests["🧪 Plan<br>Testing Approach"]
    
    %% Level 3 Planning
    DetermineLevel -->|"Level 3<br>Component Development"| L3["🏗️ Level 3:<br>Component Planning"]
    L3 --> L3Reqs["📝 Document<br>Detailed Requirements"]
    L3Reqs --> L3Arch["🏛️ Establish<br>Component Architecture"]
    L3Arch --> L3Design["🎨 Create<br>Detailed Design"]
    L3Design --> L3Interface["🔌 Define<br>Interfaces"]
    L3Interface --> L3Tasks["📋 Create<br>Implementation Plan"]
    L3Tasks --> L3Tests["🧪 Design<br>Test Strategy"]
    
    %% Level 4 Planning
    DetermineLevel -->|"Level 4<br>System Architecture"| L4["🏢 Level 4:<br>System Planning"]
    L4 --> L4Reqs["📝 Document<br>Comprehensive Requirements"]
    L4Reqs --> L4Arch["🏛️ Design<br>System Architecture"]
    L4Arch --> L4Design["🎨 Create<br>Detailed Design"]
    L4Design --> L4Interface["🔌 Define<br>System Interfaces"]
    L4Interface --> L4Tasks["📋 Create<br>Phased Implementation Plan"]
    L4Tasks --> L4Tests["🧪 Design<br>Testing Strategy"]
    L4Tests --> L4Performance["⚡ Consider<br>Performance Aspects"]
    L4Performance --> L4Security["🔒 Address<br>Security Concerns"]
    
    %% Final Steps for All Levels
    L1Approach & L2Tests & L3Tests & L4Security --> EvaluateRisks["⚠️ Evaluate<br>Risks"]
    EvaluateRisks --> EstimateEffort["⏱️ Estimate<br>Effort"]
    EstimateEffort --> DocumentPlan["📝 Finalize<br>Implementation Plan"]
    DocumentPlan --> PrepareForImpl["🔧 Prepare for<br>Implementation"]
    PrepareForImpl --> NextMode["⏭️ TRANSITION TO<br>CREATIVE MODE"]
    
    %% Styling
    style Start fill:#4da6ff,stroke:#0066cc,color:white
    style DetermineLevel fill:#d94dbb,stroke:#a3378a,color:white
    style L1 fill:#4dbb5f,stroke:#36873f,color:white
